Subject: drm/hisilicon/kirin: Allow build with COMPILE_TEST=y
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 8c59c8709e3039e31174ee4941d5ac69d81ffbb0
Patch-mainline: v6.11-rc1
